description: Use ELS to mine Elastic assets. The more ELS you hold, the greater share of each asset you can claim.
descriptionLong: ELS is Elastic’s fixed-supply governance token that primarily acts as a mechanism to participate in the entire Elastic ecosystem and benefit from the increasing demand for Elastic assets. ELS plays multiple other roles including: seeding new Elastic markets, incentivizing participation in markets and providing community-owned governance of Elastic asset economics.
